[Category "Bidding Conventions"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "bidding_conventions/jacoby_2nt_splinters"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner's 3\S bid is a Splinter, showing a singleton \S, good trump support, and 13-16 points. You bid your first-round \C control, and partner replies with 4\D.  

There isn't really anything else you want to know. You think you can make slam so you bid 6\H.}

